<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5297814>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Cratera picuia sp. n. Holotype. (A): dorsal view of the live specimen. (B): photomicrograph of a sagittal section of the pharynx. (C): photomicrograph of a sagittal section of the copulatory apparatus. (D): diagrammatic representation of the copulatory apparatus from sagittal sections." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5297814/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5297816>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Cratera picuia sp. n. Holotype. (A): photomicrograph of a sagittal section showing the intrabulbar position of the prostatic vesicle. (B): photomicrograph of a sagittal section of the tip of penis papilla. (C): photomicrograph of a sagittal section of the female genital canal and female atrium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5297816/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

